Note on source materials:
  This dataset is derived from publicly-available technical regulations
  published by Chinese government agencies (应急管理部 / 国家市场监督管理总局).
  Original regulation texts are PRC government publications and are
  not subject to copyright per PRC Copyright Law Article 5.
  The Q&A annotations and packaging in this repository are released
  under CC BY 4.0 by the dataset authors.
